      <title>最高法院裁决显示美元仍有上涨空间，美元获得额外提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/dollar-gets-extra-boost-as-supreme-court-ruling-signals-currency-has-room-to-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院一项重要裁决之后，美元上涨，凸显出如果唐纳德·特朗普再次出任总统，美元还有进一步上涨的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/dollar-gets-extra-boost-as-supreme-court-ruling-signals-currency-has-room-to-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:26:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长温施需要获得令人信服的论据，才能在 2024 年实施两次以上的降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/ecb-s-wunsch-would-need-convincing-for-more-than-two-2024-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员皮埃尔·温施 (Pierre Wunsch) 需要彻底确信通胀将回升至 2% 的目标，他才会支持今年将利率降低两次以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/ecb-s-wunsch-would-need-convincing-for-more-than-two-2024-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
